										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A major acceleration window has just opened for all point collectors on Binance Alpha! Binance is thrilled to announce a limited-time campaign that grants a </span><b>4x Trading Volume Boost</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> whenever you buy or sell bStocks via the Binance Wallet interface.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This campaign is strategically designed to help users climb the Alpha Points leaderboard four times faster than standard trading activities. This milestone also marks the mainstream debut of bStocks—the first-ever tokenized securities admitted to the FSRA Official List following regulatory prospectus approvals by the ADGM&#8217;s Financial Services Regulatory Authority.</span></p>
<h2><b>What is bStocks and How the 4x Multiplier Works</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">bStocks are innovative tokenized securities issued by BTech Holdings Limited (a Binance group affiliate). Each individual bStocks token is strictly backed 1:1 by a physical US share held securely at a regulated custodian and is publicly verifiable on-chain.</span></p>
<p><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Important structural note:</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;"> bStocks represent a direct financial interest in the underlying securities held by the Issuer; they do not represent direct voting stock or corporate ownership in the underlying listed company itself.</span></p>
